{"tid":2388554,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日大胃王女神美到不科學　性感床照外洩","createTime":"2021-01-31T08:29:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T15:06:22.000Z","uid":147522,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"be8bb7503f1ce8dd8b5548be9686bfea49f3b0dd","tid":2388554,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T08:29:07.000Z","msg":"日本娛樂圈誕生許多身形纖細，但食量卻相當驚人的「大胃王女神」，她們除了吃東西的強大的「本業」之外，隨著社群軟體的發達，她們也在網路上擁有相當高的討論度。近期，從新聞主播轉戰大胃王網紅的女星谷亞沙子（谷あさこ）就是經典案例，而她近日一套性感美圖，很快在IG引發討論。<br />\n<br />\n目前27歲的谷亞沙子，曾經展示一餐吞下98盤壽司、16碗烏龍麵等「戰績」，令人嘖嘖稱奇。近日，谷亞沙子就分享一套美圖，照片中，只見她靠在枕頭上，上半身「中空狀態」，僅用一條毛料上衣遮住；下半身則僅穿上一件內褲，模樣既居家又性感。<br />\n<br />\n這種不經意的性感，獲得大批粉絲讚賞，不少人都直言：可愛、性感；也有人對於她擁有如此驚人的食量，卻還能保持纖細身形，感到十分佩服。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oRDLXxE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoRDLXxE.jpg&h=89d36162&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10a4e0fdd8d876f8869bab52976cf86b492f0967","tid":2388554,"uid":64444,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T08:31:24.000Z","msg":"圖呢？"},{"pid":"32a499dabc3aaa523f197f6cb6a5fbb5b2113d12","tid":2388554,"uid":65774,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T08:32:27.000Z","msg":"呢個post嘅意義到底喺邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"678a7623e93e8f85e9e4c9953b5f036fcae04c73","tid":2388554,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T08:32:47.000Z","msg":"啲屎多到塞住屎坑"},{"pid":"be1f467d1bbcea894a4f9c9f841f391c9b797b44","tid":2388554,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T08:35:38.000Z","msg":"一餐吞下98盤壽司、16碗烏龍麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616e24c2189cd3687f9ab29330ec5dceaaf965bb","tid":2388554,"uid":384820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T08:3